{"tid":2410058,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國女星金所炫着韓服宣傳新劇被指「辱中」","createTime":"2021-02-16T09:59:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T06:26:53.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":60,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"e7a16b4862f2bdaf290972f7c811d5c50cdcfd4b","tid":2410058,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T09:59:50.000Z","msg":"由金所炫、金志洙和李知勳主演的新劇《月升之江》昨日（15日）開播，香港劇迷也能在「黃Viu煲劇平台」上同步追看。金所炫早前特意上傳新照宣傳，卻因身上的韓服而無辜捲入辱華風波。<br />\n<br />\n金所炫於《月升之江》飾演「平岡公主」一角，同時亦有天主房殺手「廉佳珍」的身份。日前金所炫在IG上傳拍攝的幕後照，為新劇宣傳外順道祝粉絲新年快樂。可是金所炫身上的韓服造型，卻無故惹來內地網民的不滿，指韓服是偷竊中國的文化，有抄襲中國漢服之嫌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210216/438370914019577856386214.jpeg/bhn6xpxYxCLA6uUWFZKw6bFvZRL0fLLATjsXR047F0c?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210216%2F438370914019577856386214.jpeg%2Fbhn6xpxYxCLA6uUWFZKw6bFvZRL0fLLATjsXR047F0c%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=12c5cb57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（IG/@wow_kimsohyun）<br />\n<br />\n大批內地網友翻牆到金所炫IG，除了用「Happy Chinese New Year」洗版外，亦留言表示「多謝你穿漢服慶祝中國新年」、「多謝你宣傳中國漢服」。甚至有激動網民大鬧「你們穿中國漢服真的很醜很土氣，穿自己的服裝好嗎，這麼嫌棄自己的服裝」。面對內地網民轟金所炫辱華，韓國網友認為她非常無辜，質疑韓國非首次拍史劇，為何現在才作出指責，希望大家能互相尊重各國文化。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.hk01 .com/即時娛樂/587961</code></pre>"},{"pid":"c7ebe875ea3777371a0b45c9aec42a4eed3f2370","tid":2410058,"uid":45910,"like":100,"dislike":0,"score":100,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T10:01:25.000Z","msg":"韓國又唔係自古以來係中國啦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8535b82888c8d6ea3a9898ed982a641a0cbc622e","tid":2410058,"uid":145273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T10:01:32.000Z","msg":"又辱華<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ecf5ec08db86be8da24104d7f9cbab31b0beaf1","tid":2410058,"uid":237562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T10:03:34.000Z","msg":"乜都辱華"},{"pid":"df47a285e915abe385664642b840e4d139e2ba8a","tid":2410058,"uid":92908,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T10:03:53.000Z","msg":"咁我著西裝講支那新年快樂又辱華？"},{"pid":"128b296d46d77054fdc160b4a1194e514a366678","tid":2410058,"uid":8308,"like":143,"dislike":0,"score":143,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T10:04:01.000Z","msg":"人大開會<br />\n幾千人著住西裝係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24af912617d02c9d5569dc629926eba68fc2ba2a","tid":2410058,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T10:04:15.000Z","msg":"辱支就辱支啦"},{"pid":"a253d37b62a1b53e381bd6835c0a9efa6e0a2b4d","tid":2410058,"uid":52590,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"128b296d46d77054fdc160b4a1194e514a366678","tid":2410058,"uid":8308,"like":143,"dislike":0,"score":143,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T10:04:01.000Z","msg":"人大開會<br />\n幾千人著住西裝係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T10:04:29.000Z","msg":"侮辱智慧"},{"pid":"7efd233c8633b84771418f1443e74bdf7abcc4a9","tid":2410058,"uid":166785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T10:04:40.000Z","msg":"支支又比人肉"},{"pid":"f2068b907abf36207fc20ea0cfb2da90b185bdd0","tid":2410058,"uid":23635,"like":149,"dislike":0,"score":149,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T10:05:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UmTBZpH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUmTBZpH.jpg&h=aa7d6659&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8da5557551105835f1d7abf951db22b015499ab7","tid":2410058,"uid":81113,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"128b296d46d77054fdc160b4a1194e514a3